WEBVTT

00:02.559 --> 00:04.170
<i>Previously on</i> Hawaii Five-O...

00:04.312 --> 00:06.262
What are you doing in my house?
Who are you?

00:06.264 --> 00:07.646
I'm Marco Reyes.

00:07.648 --> 00:09.782
When your brother disappeared,

00:09.784 --> 00:12.618
he was in possession of
a significant amount my money.

00:12.620 --> 00:13.786
Okay. How much money?

00:13.788 --> 00:16.155
18-and-a-half million dollars.

00:16.157 --> 00:18.874
You have until Monday to bring
my money to this address.

00:18.876 --> 00:21.160
What happens if I don't
bring you the money?

00:21.162 --> 00:24.797
You'll get a package with
your brother's head in it.

00:24.799 --> 00:25.998
<i> Three years ago,</i>
<i>Matt gets on that plane.</i>

00:26.000 --> 00:27.416
<i>Not a single piece of luggage,</i>

00:27.418 --> 00:30.169
<i>but he's supposed to have</i>
<i>18-and-a-half million dollars.</i>

00:30.171 --> 00:31.504
If that's the case,
then it's here on the island.

00:31.506 --> 00:33.005
So, what? How you
supposed to find it?

00:33.007 --> 00:34.507
About a month
after he disappeared,

00:34.509 --> 00:36.008
he sent me a postcard.

00:36.010 --> 00:37.476
Yeah? What'd it say?
Did it mention the money?

00:37.478 --> 00:38.511
No, he didn't mention the money.

00:38.513 --> 00:39.562
He just wrote,
“Wish you were here.”

00:39.564 --> 00:40.980
It was a picture
of this remote area

00:40.982 --> 00:44.233
on Oahu with a rock formation
and a couple of palm trees.

