01:21.606 --> 01:23.856
Danny!

01:25.276 --> 01:27.893
Hey, Danny?

01:27.895 --> 01:30.112
In here.

01:39.190 --> 01:42.141
Whoa.

01:42.143 --> 01:44.710
You were right.

01:44.712 --> 01:46.912
Yeah. Um...

01:46.914 --> 01:51.300
Except for the fact that, uh,
Reyes said that Matty owed him

01:51.302 --> 01:52.918
18-and-a-half million dollars.

01:52.920 --> 01:56.589
You see, this is only
$13 million.

01:56.591 --> 01:58.307
Are you sure?

01:58.309 --> 02:00.559
Yes, I am positive--
I counted it three times.

02:00.561 --> 02:03.896
So, Matty must have taken some
to help himself disappear.

02:03.898 --> 02:05.431
Yeah.

02:05.433 --> 02:06.815
And now I am, uh,

02:06.817 --> 02:08.767
five-and-a-half million
dollars short.

02:08.769 --> 02:10.769
And I have two days to come up
with all of it,

02:10.770 --> 02:13.355
or, um... my brother's dead.

02:14.775 --> 02:18.360
